---
import InstagramIcon from './icons/Instagram.astro';
import WhatsAppIcon from './icons/WhatsApp.astro';
import GmailIcon from './icons/Gmail.astro';
---

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-8 px-2 sm:px-4">
    <div class="mb-10 text-center md:text-left">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Comunidad & Partners</h2>
      <p class="text-white/50 font-mono text-[11px] sm:text-sm tracking-tighter sm:tracking-normal">
        // Alianzas estratégicas para soluciones integrales.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative group">
      <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-200 to-orange-500 rounded-3xl blur opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-30 transition duration-1000"></div>
      
      <div class="relative p-5 md:p-8 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-center md:items-start">
          
          <div class="flex-grow text-center md:text-left">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-3 mb-4">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-yellow-200 text-black text-[9px] font-bold rounded-full uppercase tracking-tighter">
                Hardware Division
              </span>
              <span class="text-white/20 font-mono text-[10px]">est. 2024</span>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3">IHP Reparaciones</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-xl text-xs md:text-base text-pretty">
              Especialistas en servicio técnico de alta complejidad. Mantenimiento de <strong>celulares, consolas y computadoras</strong>. 
              Nuestros socios en Corrientes para que tu hardware rinda al máximo.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-3">
              <a href="https://ihpweb.netlify.app/" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-white text-xs transition-all">
                <svg class="size-4 text-yellow-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" /></svg>
                <span>Web</span>
              </a>

              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ihp_reparaciones/" target="_blank" class="p-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-white transition-all">
                  <InstagramIcon class="size-4 md:size-5" />
                </a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/543795037585" target="_blank" class="p-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-white transition-all">
                  <WhatsAppIcon class="size-4 md:size-5 text-[#25D366]" />
                </a>
                <a href="mailto:ihpreparaciones@gmail.com" class="p-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-white transition-all">
                  <GmailIcon class="size-4 md:size-5 text-[#EA4335]" />
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="w-full md:w-48 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-1 gap-2 font-mono">
            <div class="p-3 bg-black/40 border border-white/5 rounded-xl">
              <p class="text-[9px] text-white/40 uppercase mb-2">Servicios</p>
              <ul class="text-[10px] text-yellow-200/80 space-y-1">
                <li>• Celulares</li>
                <li>• Consolas</li>
                <li>• PC/Notebooks</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="p-3 bg-black/40 border border-white/5 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-center">
              <p class="text-[9px] text-white/40 uppercase mb-2">Soporte</p>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-white/70 leading-tight">Mantenimiento y Limpieza Pro</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 p-4 border-l-2 border-yellow-200/30 bg-yellow-200/5 rounded-r-xl">
      <p class="text-white/60 text-[11px] md:text-sm italic leading-relaxed text-center md:text-left text-pretty">
        "En la intersección del hardware y el software nacen las soluciones reales. Trabajamos juntos para que solo te preocupes por tu negocio."
      </p>
    </div>
</div>